item.title: Finishty
item.description: So i finished my class today.. it was nice to finish.. i hung out with kinnera some more.. woohaa.. it was nice… i brought my camera to mar-riot and took pictures of some of my new friends.. it was nice.. tomarrow i drive far far away.. to colorado.. hopefully it all works out ok.. i imagine it will
